      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GERALDTON CREW (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Dazzling Dynamo (25.86) in a T3 RSTW. Has the pace to be prominent. The form out of his last race has been franked. Likely to feature again. FABULOUS JONES (1) is making her debut here for the Korie-Lee Heinrich kennel and profiles nicely. Among the leading players. YALE DOLLY (3) has her first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Among the leading players. WYONG ODHRAN (4) is by Cet Dirty Dan out of Gypsy Wyong making debut. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Can sneak into the frame at his first appearance.",
